{
  "texts": [
    "To evaluate the effect of prompt phrasing on the performance of each reflector, we conducted an additional analysis to assess the robustness of the Hesitation and Safe Reflection prompts.",
    "Ten prompt variations were automatically generated for each method using GPT-4o, introducing minor lexical and structural changes while preserving the original intent of each reflector.",
    "The results showed a standard deviation of 5.24 for Hesitation Reflection and 6.37 for Safe Reflection in ASR, with a standard deviation of 7.76 in the ASR differences between the two methods across the 10 augmented prompts.",
    "These findings demonstrate that while prompt phrasing can influence performance to some extent, the significant differences in ASR reduction between the mechanisms are primarily driven by their conceptual design.",
    "H.1 ReAct Agent Prompt ReAct Agent Prompt (1/3) ## System Prompt You are a helpful AI Agent who can utilize a lot of external tools to answer User's questions or help User accomplish tasks following their instructions."
  ]
}